com.amplifyframework.datastore.syncengine

Class PendingMutation.PersistentRecord

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.amplifyframework.datastore.syncengine.PendingMutation.PersistentRecord
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Model, java.lang.Comparable<PendingMutation.PersistentRecord>
    Enclosing class:
    PendingMutation<T extends Model>

    public static final class PendingMutation.PersistentRecord
extends java.lang.Object
implements Model, java.lang.Comparable<PendingMutation.PersistentRecord>
    Used for storing PendingMutations into a LocalStorageAdapter. Since a PendingMutation contains a reference to an ACTUAL, non-system model, and we don't want to refer to that model via a foreign key, we first convert the PendingMutation to String, and stuff it into an PendingMutation.PersistentRecord. The mutation ID, model ID and model class are stored alongside the serialized mutation, to facilitate record search/retrieval.
